MAME 0.137u1

<p>
Time to grab the <a href="http://mamedev.org/updates.html">first update to 0.137</a>.
</p>
<p>
And kindly stop harassing us if you hear that an update is coming but it hasn't been
posted yet. Each update is validated against 8 different build styles on a relatively
middle-tier system, and that validation takes a while, especially when it finds issues
(which is why we run the validation steps in the first place!) and we have to start
it all over again.
</p>
